OL,4,CPlan to ban sex education for children
OL,5,Cunder nine
OL,6,GSchools in England will be banned from
OL,7,Gteaching sex education to children
OL,8,Gunder nine, under new government
OL,9,Gguidance to be published on Thursday.
OL,11,FThe BBC has not seen the new
OL,12,Fguidelines but a government source
OL,13,Fsaid they also included plans to ban
OL,14,Fany children being taught about gender
OL,15,Fidentity.
OL,17,FHead teachers have said there is no
OL,18,Fevidence of a widespread problem with
OL,19,Fage-inappropriate materials.
OL,21,FOne union has said said the review is
OL,22,F"politically motivated".
